#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne_Classic/scenarios/00_Tutorial_part_1.cfg:1131
msgid "The quintain is destroyed, and I have gained more experience!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne_Classic/scenarios/00_Tutorial_part_1.cfg:1136
msgid ""
"Yes, you gain experience through battle, especially by killing an opponent. "
"Gain enough experience and you’ll become more powerful."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne_Classic/scenarios/00_Tutorial_part_1.cfg:1142
msgid ""
"Now, Konrad, I will leave you with more dummies to practice on! After that, "
"we have real work to do..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne_Classic/scenarios/00_Tutorial_part_1.cfg:1147
msgid ""
"Now, Li’sar, I will leave you with more dummies to practice on! After that, "
"we have real work to do..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne_Classic/scenarios/00_Tutorial_part_1.cfg:1209
msgid "Note"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne_Classic/scenarios/00_Tutorial_part_1.cfg:1211
msgid ""
"These dummies only attack if you are a single tile away. With care, you "
"should be able to kill them one at a time."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=student
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne_Classic/scenarios/00_Tutorial_part_1.cfg:1220
msgid ""
"Well, I think I know the basics. Onwards! Maybe I can fight in a real battle "
"next?"
msgstr ""

